{"title":"apollo-8.0安装教程","uid":"a77004d67ce0985b0c015233df92b27d","slug":"apollo-8-0-install","date":"2023-01-08T11:29:44.000Z","updated":"2023-08-25T02:50:39.898Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/apollo-8-0-install.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://www.loliapi.com/acg/?id=5","content":"<h1 id=\"apollo-8-0-安装教程\"><a href=\"#apollo-8-0-安装教程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"apollo 8.0 安装教程\"></a>apollo 8.0 安装教程</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>本文基于官方软件包方式<a href=\"https://apollo.baidu.com/community/Apollo-Homepage-Document/Apollo_Doc_CN_8_0?doc=/%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%25A3%2585%25E8%25AF%25B4%25E6%2598%258E/%25E8%25BD%25AF%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%25A3%2585/%25E8%25BD%25AF%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%25A3%2585\">安装教程</a></p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"更新系统\"><a href=\"#更新系统\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"更新系统\"></a>更新系统</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo apt-get update\nsudo apt-get upgrade</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"安装docker\"><a href=\"#安装docker\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装docker\"></a>安装docker</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>如果提示curl 未知 直接终端输入 <code>sudo apt-get install curl</code> 就行</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">wget http:&#x2F;&#x2F;apollo-pkg-beta.bj.bcebos.com&#x2F;docker_install.sh\nbash docker_install.sh</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"dokcer-更换国内源\"><a href=\"#dokcer-更换国内源\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"dokcer 更换国内源\"></a>dokcer 更换国内源</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>需要的更换某些情况下国内源会快一点</p></blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li><p>终端输入<code>sudo vim /etc/docker/daemon.json</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>按 <code>i</code> 进入插入编辑模式</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>复制下面的内容粘贴进终端去</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>终端粘贴命令是 ctrl + shift + v</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-json\" data-language=\"json\"><code class=\"language-json\">&#123;\n  &quot;registry-mirrors&quot;: [\n    &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;hub-mirror.c.163.com&quot;,\n    &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;ustc-edu-cn.mirror.aliyuncs.com&quot;,\n    &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;ghcr.io&quot;,\n    &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirror.baidubce.com&quot;\n  ]\n&#125;</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p>按<code>ESC</code> 退出编辑模式 输入 <code>:wq!</code> 保存并且退出</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>终端输入<code> sudo systemctl restart docker</code> 重启docker服务</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>输入<code>docker info</code> 查看是否换源成功</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>最后一段输出以下内容就是成功</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">Insecure Registries:\n 127.0.0.0&#x2F;8\nRegistry Mirrors:\n https:&#x2F;&#x2F;hub-mirror.c.163.com&#x2F;\n https:&#x2F;&#x2F;ustc-edu-cn.mirror.aliyuncs.com&#x2F;\n https:&#x2F;&#x2F;ghcr.io&#x2F;\n https:&#x2F;&#x2F;mirror.baidubce.com&#x2F;\nLive Restore Enabled: false\n   </code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"安装Apollo-包管理工具\"><a href=\"#安装Apollo-包管理工具\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Apollo 包管理工具\"></a>安装Apollo 包管理工具</h2><ol>\n<li><p>添加apt 源</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo bash -c &quot;echo &#39;deb https:&#x2F;&#x2F;apollo-pkg-beta.cdn.bcebos.com&#x2F;neo&#x2F;beta bionic main&#39; &gt;&gt; &#x2F;etc&#x2F;apt&#x2F;sources.list&quot;\nwget -O - https:&#x2F;&#x2F;apollo-pkg-beta.cdn.bcebos.com&#x2F;neo&#x2F;beta&#x2F;key&#x2F;deb.gpg.key | sudo apt-key add -\nsudo apt update</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p>安装aem 工具</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo apt install apollo-neo-env-manager-dev</code></pre>\n\n\n</li>\n<li><p>输入<code>aem -h</code> 查看是否安装成功</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>看到以下输出就是成功</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">Usage:\n    aem [OPTION]\n\nOptions:\n    start : start a docker container with apollo development image.\n    start_gpu : start a docker container with apollo gpu support development image.\n    enter : enter into the apollo development container.\n    stop : stop all apollo development container.\n    install_core : install the core module of apollo.\n    bootstrap : run dreamview and monitor module.\n    build : build package in workspace.\n    install : install package in workspace.\n    init: init single workspace. \n    update: update core modules of apollo.</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"安装英伟达驱动\"><a href=\"#安装英伟达驱动\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装英伟达驱动\"></a>安装英伟达驱动</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>如果仅仅学习规划和控制就没必要安装英伟达驱动捏,当然你要想看看有无gpu是否有区别，也可以装</p></blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li><p>安装英伟达驱动</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo apt-get update \nsudo apt-add-repository multiverse \nsudo apt-get update \nsudo apt-get install nvidia-driver-455</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p>安装完了输入<code>nvidia-smi </code> 查看是否安装成功</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">Sun Jan  8 19:54:14 2023       \n+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| NVIDIA-SMI 525.60.11    Driver Version: 525.60.11    CUDA Version: 12.0     |\n|-------------------------------+----------------------+----------------------+\n| GPU  Name        Persistence-M| Bus-Id        Disp.A | Volatile Uncorr. ECC |\n| Fan  Temp  Perf  Pwr:Usage&#x2F;Cap|         Memory-Usage | GPU-Util  Compute M. |\n|                               |                      |               MIG M. |\n|&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D;&